Replacing the solenoid MultiBloc MB-...B0...

1. Switch off firing system.

3. Replace solenoid Important: Make sure that the solenoid no. and voltage are correct!

4. Remount hydraulic brake or ad- justing plate as described on page 2/3:"Replacing the hydraulic brake or adjusting plate", steps 7 -11.

5. Switch on firing system.

Remplacement de la bobine MultiBloc MB-...B0...

1. Mettre l´installation hors tension.
